Zen Hero - Habit Tracker App - Legal Information: Zen Hero is here to help to track and manage personal habits. However Zen Hero will not ask you to pay using any ways except using payments through Apple App Store. Also, Zen Hero does not require to submit any users personal data. All data inputted by user is stored only locally on users device and in iCloud in that way so Zen Hero cannot access users data. Zen Hero cannot be held responsible for any successfull or unsuccessfull notifiying about users inputted data, such as notifications about future subscriptions or payments.
